{"hash":"dba4df3083778d400479dfdd020ec321dc5376cc","data":{"tags":{"edges":[{"node":{"id":"Technical writing","title":"Technical writing","path":"/tag/technical-writing/"}},{"node":{"id":"Project Management","title":"Project Management","path":"/tag/project-management/"}},{"node":{"id":"Product Management","title":"Product Management","path":"/tag/product-management/"}},{"node":{"id":"Mindfulness & Mental Health","title":"Mindfulness & Mental Health","path":"/tag/mindfulness-and-mental-health/"}},{"node":{"id":"Front-end development","title":"Front-end development","path":"/tag/front-end-development/"}}]},"doc":{"content":"<h1 id=\"contact\"><a href=\"#contact\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"icon icon-link\"></span></a>Contact</h1>\n<p>Hey, thanks for stopping by my little nook.</p>\n<p>I enjoy writing about and developing things that help people make their daily lives a little easier. So if there's anything you think I can help with, then please <a href=\"#get-in-touch\">get in touch</a> or <a href=\"#schedule-a-call\">schedule a call</a>.</p>\n<p>And while you're here, if there's I've written that makes you want to do better work, please consider <a href=\"#donate\">leaving a donation</a>.</p>\n<h2 class=\"big\" id=\"something-i-can-help-with\"><a href=\"#something-i-can-help-with\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"icon icon-link\"></span></a>Something I can help with?</h2>\n<p><img class=\"g-image g-image--lazy g-image--loading\" src=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3csvg fill='none' viewBox='0 0 883 712' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' xmlns:xlink='http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink'%3e%3cdefs%3e%3cfilter id='__svg-blur-49d7f05ec63c8d5396d9a7454205d879'%3e%3cfeGaussianBlur in='SourceGraphic' stdDeviation='40'/%3e%3c/filter%3e%3c/defs%3e%3cimage x='0' y='0' filter='url(%23__svg-blur-49d7f05ec63c8d5396d9a7454205d879)' width='883' height='712' xlink:href='data:image/svg%2bxml%3bbase64%2ciVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAEAAAAA0CAYAAAA62j4JAAAACXBIWXMAAAsTAAALEwEAmpwYAAAO7UlEQVRo3u