wBYYSB1oeBQNzu3LnjgCi4c8cVXGYw/C0S8BG4vxVOIal0nq2urqcLFfT31wjVDTWOG2NVPVoEWjNCVGodcCwD4P8YPMJ77IPOSpXq4v8A1o9IxIsA9rAAAAAASUVORK5CYII=' /%3e%3c/svg%3e\" width=\"883\" alt=\"support\" data-srcset=\"/assets/static/support.82a2fbd.24d53c73dd65119dfc631fd3648af4a6.svg 480w, /assets/static/support.182e2b4.24d53c73dd65119dfc631fd3648af4a6.svg 883w\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 883px) 100vw, 883px\" data-src=\"/assets/static/support.182e2b4.24d53c73dd65119dfc631fd3648af4a6.svg\"><noscript><img class=\"g-image g-image--lazy g-image--loaded\" src=\"/assets/static/support.182e2b4.24d53c73dd65119dfc631fd3648af4a6.svg\" width=\"883\" alt=\"support\"></noscript></p>\n<h3 id=\"get-in-touch\"><a href=\"#get-in-touch\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"icon icon-link\"></span></a>Get in touch</h3>\n<p>Send me an email, text, or leave a voicemail.</p>\n<p><strong>Phone</strong> <a href=\"tel:+16466942062\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">+1 ‪ (646) 694-2062</a></p>\n<p><strong>Email</strong> <a href=\"mailto:mscotthendricks@gmail.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">mscotthendricks@gmail.com</a></p>\n<p><strong>Location</strong> <a href=\"https://www.google.com/maps/place/Seattle,+WA+98125\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Seattle WA (98125)</a></p>\n<h3 id=\"send-me-a-note\"><a href=\"#send-me-a-note\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"icon icon-link\"></span></a>Send me a note</h3>\n<p>Project in mind? Or need some help with documentation? Want to share your thoughts about an article I wrote? Reach out using your name, email, and a brief message (or <a href=\"#schedule-a-call\">schedule a call</a> instead.)</p>\n<div>\n  <form action=\"https://formspree.io/mayprbyk\" method=\"POST\">\n    <div class=\"sender-info\">\n      <div class=\"group\">\n        <label for=\"name\" class=\"form-input-label\">Your name</label>\n        <input required class=\"form-input\" type=\"text\" name=\"name\" />\n      </div>\n     